    <task id="LOCAL-00004" summary="OreCzml V2.0 changes :&#10;- Name reworked : OreCZML -&gt; OreCzml&#10;- Repository root renamed : org.example -&gt; org.orekit.czml&#10;- JavaDoc of all classes added.&#10;- Renamed : CZMLFile -&gt; CzmlFile.&#10;- REWORK : renamed generateCZML() -&gt; writeCZMLBlock() . The writeCZMLBlocks function will be called directly in the CZMLFile.java instead of each time a primary object is added.&#10;- REWORK : The user only need to build a CzmlFile now, add the objects with the addObject(Object) function then call CzmlFile.write();&#10;- Add the AbstractPrimaryObject class to add a layer and a common ground for each PrimaryObject.&#10;- Added scr/tutorial for future tutorials added here.&#10;- The OreCzml main for test is now in tutorials.&#10;- Added LowEarthOrbitSatellite tutorial in Tutorials.&#10;- Header object can no longer be built with a propagator.&#10;- Renamed CZMLGroundStation -&gt; CzmlGroundStation&#10;- CzmlGroundStation can no longer be built with an Orekit groundStation.&#10;- A directory CzmlEnum has been created for each enum used.&#10;- Add a presentation image for the Readme.md&#10;- A Header.MASTER_CLOCK is not available to be used as a global clock.">
